snippet.title: Svoboda 1945: Liberation - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: The WW2 is over but there’s no peace. Historical adventure taking place in the Czech borderlands. Reveal the scars of the past and forgotten injustices. Where’s the line between revenge and justice? And would you think the same if your family was involved? Learn more at https://www.svoboda1945.com/ and http://bit.ly/SvobodaOnSteam
